00:03:26.840 --> 00:03:28.093
Scenario 1.

00:03:28.680 --> 00:03:29.680
A young lady,

00:03:30.540 --> 00:03:32.237
let's call her Ada.

00:03:32.238 --> 00:03:34.051
Ada is on her way back from work,

00:03:34.651 --> 00:03:42.301
and she comes across a restaurant
carrying out a marketing or a publicity

00:03:42.420 --> 00:03:46.207
for their new kitchen,
for their new restaurant.

00:03:46.747 --> 00:03:50.280
They hand her a flyer,
and they say, "Please check us out.

00:03:50.910 --> 00:03:56.723
Our food is sumptuous,
our food, you'd love it."

00:03:56.724 --> 00:03:58.477
Ada agrees.

00:03:58.478 --> 00:04:01.501
She collects the flyer
from their hand, and she goes home.

00:04:03.061 --> 00:04:04.200
One day, she's hungry,

00:04:04.201 --> 00:04:07.225
and she remembers, "Oh, there's a flyer
I got from a new restaurant.

00:04:07.226 --> 00:04:09.031
I would love
to try out this new restaurant."

00:04:09.750 --> 00:04:11.838
She checks out the flyer.

00:04:12.450 --> 00:04:13.770
