Interesting.

00:04:15.661 --> 00:04:19.503
The food imagery used,
very beautiful, enticing.

00:04:19.504 --> 00:04:22.861
It's making her feel hungry,
and she has decided,

00:04:22.951 --> 00:04:24.196
"I want to order."

00:04:25.081 --> 00:04:29.100
Now, Ada is looking
for the contact details of this restaurant

00:04:29.101 --> 00:04:31.801
to place the order,
but she's unable to find it.

00:04:32.581 --> 00:04:37.620
Let us add that Ada is someone
with visual impairments,

00:04:37.890 --> 00:04:39.091
so she has low vision.

