00:05:14.520 --> 00:05:17.430
The shopping mall is a mall for children,

00:05:17.971 --> 00:05:20.400
and he's taken by his guardian
to pick out clothing.

00:05:21.421 --> 00:05:27.408
At the entrance of the shopping mall
is a big banner where the brand

00:05:27.409 --> 00:05:29.250
is advertising their clothes line

00:05:30.480 --> 00:05:31.480
for children.

00:05:32.221 --> 00:05:36.090
Obi sees beautiful faces of children
just like him,

00:05:36.450 --> 00:05:37.450
about his age,

00:05:38.041 --> 00:05:39.301
different races,

00:05:39.481 --> 00:05:40.771
different gender,

00:05:41.701 --> 00:05:42.990
but something is missing.

00:05:44.160 --> 00:05:45.929
He doesn't see anybody like him.

00:05:45.930 --> 00:05:46.671
Why?

00:05:46.672 --> 00:05:49.610
